* System requirements

MySQL tables (/var/lib/mysql) : ~3GB
Data (~trait) : ~3GB
OS: Ubuntu Hardy (8.04)
Memory: 256MB

* Installation

** Create user
** As the new user:
*** git clone git://github.com/xwu/trait-o-matic.git
*** cd trait-o-matic/script
*** ./install-root.sh # requires sudo ability
*** ./install-user.sh
*** reboot, or sudo /etc/init.d/trait.sh start
